description.description: Added to Students’ Gymkhana in 2016-17, the President’s Office primarily assists the President in discharging his/her duties. The council consists of President’s nominee to various institute level committees, Heads of multiple assets like the Students’ Activity Center, Students’ Server, Council finances, Managers of miscellaneous events like Nostalgia, Melange and various committees which are formed throughout the year to assist the President, Students’ Gymkhana
